// a0.  For SYS_open above the C wrapper puts the path in a0 (arg1) -> reg[4].
// Fix: use a0 for the path.
// (handled by overriding below)

// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Main execution loop (PC/nPC model handles branch delay slots naturally).
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
